game.name: Elsa Police Style
game.description:
Wow! Elsa has got an opportunity to serve her city as a police officer. She looks pretty excited after becoming a cop. Today is a first day of her job, so she does not want to make a single mistake. So, the princess needs your help to pick up the nice outfit. Would you come forward and help this beautiful lady? Join Elsa Police Style game and get ready to help dress her up and prepare for this most awaited day! Her wardrobe will have all the needful things to help you out.
Choose from a wide range of cool uniform options that you would see at the left corner of the screen in this brand new dressing game for girls! There are various batons, handcuffs, as well as uniforms and hats. Dress her up with a white shirt and blue pant and combine her look with a matching blue color shoes! A green color dress above the knees will also look perfect on the girl. She will also look amazing in white shirt combined with a blue jacket and blue pant. Do not forget to select a matching goggle for the lady.
There is no shortage for a wonderful range of shoes and police cap and a stick. Click the replay button to start the fun from the scratch or hit the right click button to see the final result in this html5 princess dress-up game! Being a princess, she does not know how to pick up a cop outfit. So, it is up to you that how put your best to prepare the lady for this important day. All the best to have a blast in our kids games that are available to play for free, no download required!
